cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on recognizing text entailment for Arabic language. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses sentiment analysis, which falls under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of machine learning algorithms to improve the accuracy of text entailment also suggests the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval and decision making, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
